<stack-static>
    <statement><p><p>
Given that:
<me>
\log_{10}(x) = {3}
</me>
</p>

<p>
Find the value of <m>x</m>.
</p>

<p>
<m>x</m> = <fillin characters="8" name="ans1"/>  
</p></p></statement>
    <solution><p><h3>Worked Solution</h3>

<p>
We are given:
</p>

<p>
<me>
\log_{10}(x) = {3}
</me>
</p>

<p>
To find <m>x</m>, we take the antilogarithm.
</p>

<p>
Step 1: Write in exponential form.
</p>

<p>
<me>
x = 10^{3}
</me>
</p>

<p>
Step 2: Evaluate.
</p>

<p>
<me>
x = {1000}
</me>
</p></p></solution>
    <answer><p><m>1000</m></p></answer>
</stack-static>